article.description: Bryson Williams posted 19 points and seven rebounds as UTEP topped Arkansas-Pine Bluff 59-50 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Williams scores 19 to carry UTEP past Ark.-Pine Bluff 59-50
article.linkText: Williams scores 19 to carry UTEP past Ark.-Pine Bluff 59-50
article.story: EL PASO, Texas -- Bryson Williams posted 19 points and seven rebounds as UTEP topped Arkansas-Pine Bluff 59-50 on Saturday night. Souley Boum added nine points for the Miners (6-1). Marquell Carter had 21 points and seven rebounds for the Golden Lions (1-7), who scored only 16 points in the second half. UTEP plays NC A&T next Monday. Arkansas-Pine Bluff plays Oregon State on the road next Saturday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
